      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl05_LabelName\"><sub style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary);\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);\" src=\"systems/sfrpg/images/cup/gameplay/graviton.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />&nbsp;</sub></span><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl05_LabelName\">Graviton Revelation</span><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl05_LabelName\"><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"><br /></span>As a move action, you can draw on the properties of dark matter to increase your density, allowing you to resist physical damage. You gain damage reduction 1/&mdash;. This increases to DR 2/&mdash; at 6th level and increases by 1 again every 3 solarian levels thereafter. This benefit lasts for 1 round or until you leave graviton mode. When you are attuned or fully attuned, your DR from dark matter is equal to half your solarian level.</span></p>\n<p><br /><em>Currently, the modifier in Modifiers tab will need be to be opened then saved to update Damage Reduction. This required whenever activating/deactivating this feature, or attuning/unattuning.</em></p>"
